{"tid":936300,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩幫2個摩門教鬼佬含撚","createTime":"2018-12-10T15:58:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-10T16:12:17.000Z","uid":120847,"like":15,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b2a47bbee4a8d403e1cfeacda56d37dbdfaf9939","tid":936300,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T15:58:01.000Z","msg":"岩岩放工返屋企途中俾2個摩門教鬼仔截住 兩個都好後生23,4歲嘅靚鬼仔<br />\n問我有冇思考過人生意義 <br />\n話想同我講下耶穌 <br />\n點知講講下問我去唔去佢屋企查經<br />\n我見冇野做咪跟埋去<br />\n上到去佢2個夾住我係中間 話同我祈禱<br />\n襯佢地合埋對眼姨姨暗暗 我咪一野渣落佢地條野到<br />\n佢地即刻開眼 我繼續渣<br />\n之後佢地主動企起身拉低褲鏈 拎條野出黎磨我塊面 我咪乘住個勢一野含落去 <br />\n含完左邊果條又含下右邊個條 然後2個一齊就射晒落我到 咁岩冇紙巾 佢地就撕左幾頁馬太福音落黎抹我面上啲精<br />\n又話下次再上黎一齊祈禱"},{"pid":"ac8e43ff0e301b4eec8e5f52adb93d147c0747d5","tid":936300,"uid":17677,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T15:59:16.000Z","msg":"大佬呀 好心你唔好咁癡線啦"},{"pid":"6a032737f3b57ba5614a22e0be98368e3ea776c6","tid":936300,"uid":127929,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T16:01:10.000Z","msg":"矮撚的悲嗚: 只係可以做含個個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52214502a954b865960457b30a1e44aa0ac52ae9","tid":936300,"uid":6219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T16:03:46.000Z","msg":"其實你都幾癲"},{"pid":"45efd6a3cef24eb78fac22d208ac5d04ae067a36","tid":936300,"uid":145258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T16:06:45.000Z","msg":"零分 重作。"},{"pid":"3f884f2abb274e366d5f679b32a5b8932949cdad","tid":936300,"uid":203417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T16:06:48.000Z","msg":"撕耶利米哀歌啦"},{"pid":"d675d62c9e85af8625a18301803a6d787adb00cf","tid":936300,"uid":134549,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T16:07:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a30bae9c3722ea13ac2d9b4739e08cfe2b376557","tid":936300,"uid":197484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T16:08:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/don